tate advice, help buying yachts, etc. But basically you are outsourcing you=
r wealth management to someone who works for the bank and who has other cli=
ents.</li> <li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Set up a=C2=A0<em>family offic=
e</em>, where you hire full-time professionals to run your money for you. T=
