worked at hedge funds or private equity firms before coming to work for you=
. And you pay them like investors, not with some annual fee but with a lar=
ge salary and bonus and a stake in the upside of your investments.=C2=A0</l=
i></ol><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Which will get you the best performance=
