verage group Jacobs Douwe Egberts. And they branched into coffee on-the-go =
with a series of fast-casual restaurants, buying Krispy Kreme, Panera Bread=
 and Pret A Manger. =E2=80=A6</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CI=E2=
=80=99m not afraid of taking risks,=E2=80=9D he said in an interview for a =
2011 Harvard Business School profile, describing his investing approach. =
=E2=80=9CI=E2=80=99m not afraid of losing. I=E2=80=99m not afraid of buying=
