=E2=80=94 has become its weak spot. Last year, the company returned 3% comp=
ared to 17% for the equal-weighted MSCI World Index, which it uses as its b=
enchmark.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also now it=E2=80=99=
s getting into insurance. (I mean, further into insurance, beyond the pet i=
