ed index funds and the guys who manage my money make one basis point=E2=80=
=9D: Ehh fine whatever.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">At the highes=
t levels, it is can be hard to distinguish investment from consumption. Own=
ing a sports team, or a Leonardo, is clearly both. Having a family office t=
hat makes its employees billionaires and owns =E2=80=9Cdozens of beauty lab=
