. If I had $25 billion and you offered me the choice of (1) index funds or=
 (2) this whole thing, with the underperformance and the billionaire manage=
rs and the pet insurance and the coffee empire, I would <em>unhesitatingly=
=C2=A0</em>take this whole thing. This is a better story! If you have $25=
=C2=A0billion you don=E2=80=99t=C2=A0<em>need=C2=A0</em>a few extra basis p=
oints of performance. You need to have some coherent, or entertainingly inc=
